pages.title: WeCloudData Alumni Mentors Application Survey
pages.description:
Thank you for being an amazing WeCloudData alumnus! In the past months and years, you helped us with general inquiries, support, guest lectures, referrals, etc. We're not only proud to see your progression as a data professional, but also grateful to know you're making a positive impact and helping us spread the word. We recently launched our sister institution WeCareer, a startup focusing on providing career mentorship to job applicants. As usual, we want to set the standards and become the best in what we do. And we want you to be part of it!

Please help fill out the following survey to indicate your interest, specialty, availability along with your current bio. 

We're excited that our paths cross again and let's build something amazing together!

headings.heading: Are you interested in becoming a mentor at WeCareer/WeCloudData?
Which program did you take at WeCloudData?
When did you graduate from the program?
What is your current job title?
Are you currently in a people manager position? (team lead/manager/director,e tc.)
Which area of mentorship would you like to be engaged in?

choices.text: Early career mentorship (first month on the job)

headings.heading: What type of clients/students do you want to provide services to?
Do you have an industry preference when it comes to pairing up with a student/client?
What is your availability in general?
Do you speak other languages?
Please leave your contact information
